                of ownership.</li>
            <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> DRC prioritizes confidentiality, ensuring sensitive information remains private.</li>
            <li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> The process is informal and flexible, tailored to the specific needs of the parties.</li>
            <li><strong>Mediation and Arbitration:</strong> DRC employs methods such as mediation or arbitration to reach
                resolutions.</li>
            <li><strong>Cost-Effectiveness:</strong> Resolving disputes through DRC can be quicker and more cost-effective than
                traditional litigation.</li>
            <li><strong>Preservation of Relationships:</strong> DRC emphasizes preserving relationships between the parties.</li>
        </ul>

